com.uber.simplestore.primitive

Interface PrimitiveSimpleStore

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.io.Closeable, SimpleStore

    public interface PrimitiveSimpleStore
extends SimpleStore
    Store primitives on disk.

    All methods never return null in the ListenableFuture, #SimpleStore.contains(String) should be used for optionality. If the value is not set, the 0-byte primitive will be returned.
